    {
      "text": "%md\n# NYC Yellow Taxi 2024 — EDA Dashboard\n**Course:** CSCI461 Introduction to Big Data (Spring 2026)  \n**Tool:** Apache Zeppelin 0.10.1 — Visualization / Reporting  \n**Data source:** HDFS — `hdfs://namenode:9000/taxi/raw/`  \n**Dataset:** 35,602,215 rows × 25 columns (after preprocessing)",
