            "type": "HTML",
            "data": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"markdown-body\"\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003eNYC Yellow Taxi 2024 — EDA Dashboard\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCourse:\u003c/strong\u003e CSCI461 Introduction to Big Data (Spring 2026)\u003cbr /\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eTool:\u003c/strong\u003e Apache Zeppelin 0.10.1 — Visualization / Reporting\u003cbr /\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eData source:\u003c/strong\u003e HDFS — \u003ccode\u003ehdfs://namenode:9000/taxi/raw/\u003c/code\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDataset:\u003c/strong\u003e 35,602,215 rows × 25 columns (after preprocessing)\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e"
