      "text": "%md\n## Summary\n\n| Visualisation | Chart Type | Key Finding |\n|---|---|---|\n| Trips by hour | Bar chart | Peak demand at 6 PM (2,555,714 trips); lowest at 4 AM |\n| Monthly stats | Bar chart | Highest fares in September ($20.72 avg) |\n| Payment type | Pie chart | Credit card dominates (~68% of trips) |\n| Top locations | Bar chart | Location IDs 132, 161, 237 are busiest |\n| Weekend vs Weekday | Bar chart | Weekdays have more trips; weekends have higher avg fares |\n\n**Data source:** `hdfs://namenode:9000/taxi/raw/`  \n**Visualization tool:** Apache Zeppelin 0.10.1",
